name: Chorus Aviation Inc. Voting and Variable Voting Shares
longDescription: Chorus Aviation Inc is a Canadian holding company. It aims to deliver regional aviation to the world through its businesses. It specializes in contract flying, maintenance, repair and overhaul, and aircraft leasing solutions. The company operates in two segments namely, Regional Aviation Services and Regional Aircraft Leasing. It generates maximum revenue from the Regional Aviation Services segment.
